    "---\n",
    "## 13. Handle Missing Values Introduced by Lag and Rolling Operations\n",
    "\n",
    "Lag and rolling features naturally create missing values at the beginning of each reactor sequence.\n",
    "\n",
    "For example:\n",
    "\n",
    "- a 10-step lag cannot be computed for the first 10 observations\n",
    "- rolling standard deviation may be missing at the beginning\n",
    "\n",
    "A simple and common approach is to drop rows with these newly introduced missing values before modeling."
   ]
